Troubleshooting Tips
ZAP won't start:

Ensure Java 11+ is installed: java -version
Check if port 8080 is available: netstat -tuln | grep 8080
Kill existing ZAP processes: pkill -f zap
ffuf returns no results:

Verify target is accessible: curl -I http://localhost/DVWA
Check wordlist exists: ls -lh ~/wordlists/common.txt
Reduce thread count with -t 10 if getting errors
Python scripts fail:

Install required modules: pip3 install requests
Check Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.6+)
Verify file permissions: chmod +x script.py
DVWA not accessible:

Restart Apache: sudo systemctl restart apache2
Check MySQL: sudo systemctl status mysql
Verify database setup: sudo mysql -e "SHOW DATABASES;"
